Zeltia’s Noscira Unit to Sell 800,000 New Shares at EU1 a Share

-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 
2011-09-19T16:49:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/zeltia-s-noscira-unit-to-sell-800-000-new-shares-at-eu1-a-share.html
Zeltia SA (ZEL) ’s Noscira unit will offer
800,000 new shares for 1 euro each in a capital increase, Zeltia
said in a regulatory filing. The shares will be offered first to
existing shareholders and then to other investors who are
prepared to buy at least 50,000 euros of the stock.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Sills at 
 bsills@bloomberg.net  